# Unity minimal repository (allowlist style)
# Ignore everything by default, then explicitly include required folders/files.
*

# Keep this file
!.gitignore

# Unity required project content
!Assets/
!Assets/**
!Packages/
!Packages/**
!ProjectSettings/
!ProjectSettings/**

# Exclude generated/editor junk even inside included paths
*.sln
*.csproj
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.mp4
**/*.mov
**/*.webm
**/*.avi
**/*.m4v

# Keep git internals excluded
.git/
